<topic id="relational-sql-execution-support">
  <title>SQL Execution Support</title>
  <prolog>
    <metadata>
      <keywords>
        <indexterm>Databases<indexterm>SQL support</indexterm></indexterm>
      </keywords>
    </metadata>
  </prolog>
  <body>
    <p>The database support in <ph keyref="product"/> includes support for writing SQL statements,
      syntax highlighting, <xref keyref="glossentry_foldable-elements"><term>folding</term></xref>,
      and dragging and dropping from the <xref
        href="relational-database-explorer.dita#relational-database-explorer"><uicontrol>Data Source
          Explorer</uicontrol> view</xref>. It also includes transformation scenarios for executing
      the statements, and the results are displayed in the <xref
        href="relational-table-explorer.dita#relational-table-explorer"><uicontrol>Table
          Explorer</uicontrol> view</xref>.</p>
  </body>
</topic>